solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public int removeDuplicates(int[] nums) {--newline--        int i = nums.length > 0 ? 1 : 0;--newline--        for (int n : nums)--newline--            if (n > nums[i-1])--newline--                nums[i++] = n;--newline--        return i;--newline--    }--newline--}
